/**
 * recommendationService — deterministic bounded recommendation generation.
 *
 * These recommendations are pre-defined, bounded, and non-authoritative.
 * They are selected based on risk flags — not generated by AI.
 * They are then passed to AI for explanation/contextualization only.
 *
 * All suggestion language is intentionally non-authoritative.
 */

